@cccrrraaazzziii wrote:

To make Admins, that requires you to pop into your characters folder, open up the character you mant to make Admin,

[CHARACTER] character-height = character-posx = character-posy = character-rights = 3 <--- Put 3 here for Admin (Owner) or 2 For just Admin. character-ismember = character-messages = character-lastconnection = character-lastlogin = character-energy = character-gametime = character-gamecount =

Save as, compile and run.

Note~Keep the characters file up as people experience problems with this .
